name: Smartphone Car Control UI
description:
Hey Community,


Here is the Neumorphism demo of car application where user has the following features:

  • Average Petrol Used
  • Petrol Graph of a month
  • Available Petrol
  • Average Distance travelled
  • Total Distance Covered
  • Tyre Pressure Check
  • Notifications


Hope you will like it.


Cheers!
